{{Quote|''A cozy autumnal-themed world to travel through the clouds and watch the falling leaves․''}}

'''Autumn Flash''' is a seasonal themed cross-platform world, created by DavidsonVROOM. It was published on September 21st, 2024. The world features a lodge on a wooden platform, floating in the sky with other floating homes and platforms at various altitudes. 

==Overview==
[[File:Autumn flash outside.webp|thumb|A wide-eye lens capture of the floating lodge.]][[File:Autumn flash rooftop.webp|thumb|A camera capture of the rooftop and chimney.]]
Spawning in Autumn Flash will set you outside, high up in the sky on a wooden platform. The outside has trees, high wind, and falling leaves being carried by the wind. The platform also features a two-story lodge, consisting of wooden furniture, potted plants, and a kitchen on the first floor, then a bedroom with balcony on the second floor. A ladder to the roof.

